Message.Msg: This important thing to remember about the 3-day weekend is that, in an "uptrend market" the Market Makers (banks & brokers) want all of the strong issues to end at ALL TIME HIGHS before the 3-day holiday weekend. Good professional traders know this and will trade this info accordingly. Upon return from the 3-day holiday, the following trading day will rally for half the day and sell off in the afternoon. This is all "normal stock market behavior". Happy investing to you Speak W. L. & remember to enjoy the holiday
